brief resume: ``Ex-Congressman. Director. Internal Audit@USAF
major. Have talent-experience. Call E.L.K.''
   The ad _ which says Konnyu is seeking employment as a board
member, executive or consultant _ is appearing in the national
paper this week.
   Voters last year made Konnyu, a first-term Republican, the only
member of Congress to lose his seat in the 1988 primaries.
